title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 28 2022

description:
Anti-mask mom's school board speech goes viral. Want some good news? Check out the Georgia polls. Glenn Beck joins Clay in Glenn's Dallas studio to talk with C&B about his artifact and memorabilia collection, living in Texas, his new book, The Great Reset, and more for a lively close to the show.
